column19: Goodbye... I loved... you all... so much...
Damn it... Not like this. Lucina, live on...
That's a lot of blood... Ha, ha... ha...
Why does everything have to go wrong for me?
Not cool... Not cool at all...
Master Yen'fay... I can't go on...
Shit, dying in a place like this... won't... do...
Ugh... Lucina, keep up the fight.
I face death with austerity and gladness.
Ouch... That's... a lot of blood...
